Lab: Hb 7.2 (baseline unknown), Plt 78,000, INR 1.8, BUN 48, Cr 1.0, Bilirubin 3.4, Albumin 2.4, AST 92, ALT 48, Ammonia 68
FAST: moderate ascites'
