V/S: BP 102/64 on norepi 0.15 mcg/kg/min, HR 102, RR 26 on mechanical ventilation, P/F ratio 142, Temp 37.8°C
Lab: Hb 9.4, WBC 16,800, Plt 88,000, Cr 2.6 (baseline 1.0), Lactate 2.4 (down from 6.2)
