Fasting glucose 110 (cutoff > 92), 1-hr 188 (cutoff > 180), 2-hr 168 (cutoff > 153) — 75g OGTT IADPSG criteria, 2 of 3 abnormal confirms GDM
A1c 5.8% (normal)
BMI 28, weight gain ตามเกณฑ์
