  'orthopedics', 'ems_mgmt', 'trauma', 'adult',
  'UK National Hip Fracture Database; Cochrane Reviews; AAOS Hip Fracture Guidelines', 'AI-generated-board-seed', true, 'seeded via Claude Code session (no critique pass)'
